1. Introduction
The goal of this repository is to implement python code that does analysis of arbitrary text in Mandarin, extraction of han characters/words and matching to one of the predefined word classes.

2. Word classes
3. Approach
4. Source files
 - openai_sentence_generator.py: generates sentences in english using gpt4 engine, the prompts requires that the sentences have at least one of the words from the specified word category.
 - translate_mandarin_separate.py: translates each of generated sentences to mandarin using google translate api and tokenizes it using stanza library
 - translate_to_english.py: translates the tokens of the sentences to english using google translate aptokens of the sentences to english using google translate aptokens of the sentences to english using google translate api
 
